    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "74c6bdc8-b6ca-472e-90d4-14e2e4889c43",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Clone Conundrum",
        "Location": "LOCATION_ELEGANT_LLAMA",
        "PublicId": "131970985624",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/elegant/scene_llama.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 2d206606-b1ac-4dd8-bdb6-5261d7ff0574).Image",
        "Description": "This is an odd assignment, 47. Then again, most of what we do could be considered odd, could it? \r\rReports indicate that a guest at Don Yate&apos;s retirement party has made a breakthrough in human cloning.  The downside is that the clones have gone rogue, and are now conspiring against the original. They are currently seeking partners who share the same sentiment, with their end goal being to create an army of clones.\r\rAgain, this is an odd assignment, but nothing you can&apos;t handle. Good luck, 47.",
